<inglise> Article 9 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 9 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Where the amount of compensatory aid which is to be granted for any annual instalment divided by the estimated number of agricultural holdings concerned is below EUR 400, that amount may be granted for measures concerning the agricultural sector: </inglise>
<eesti> Kui &uuml;ksk&otilde;ik millise iga-aastase osamakse puhul on asjaomaste p&otilde;llumajandusettev&otilde;tete eeldatava arvuga jagatud tasandustoetuse summa v&auml;iksem kui 400 eurot, v&otilde;ib sellise summa anda p&otilde;llumajandussektori meetmetena, </eesti>
<inglise> - which are collective and of general interest, </inglise>
