<inglise> Article 10 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 10 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> This Title lays down the detailed rules for granting the compensatory aid referred to in Article 5 of Regulation (EC) No 2799/98. </inglise>
