<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The maximum amounts of compensatory aid shall be determined in accordance with Article 5(2) of Regulation (EC) No 2799/98. </inglise>
<eesti> Tasandustoetuse maksimaalsuurus m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks vastavalt m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2799/98 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikele 2. </eesti>
<inglise> If, for the amounts mentioned in paragraph 3 of the present Article, an amount fixed in national currency is lower than the ceiling, a reduction of the ceiling which does not affect the fixed amount is not to be considered as a reduction. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui k&auml;esoleva artikli l&otilde;ikes 3 nimetatud summade puhul on omav&auml;&auml;ringus kinnitatud summa &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;rast madalam, ei k&auml;sitleta langemisena sellist piirm&auml;&auml;ra langemist, mis ei m&otilde;juta kinnitatud summat. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of Article 5 of Regulation (EC) No 2799/98, amounts of a structural or environmental character that are not: </inglise>
