<inglise> 5. </inglise>
<eesti> 5. </eesti>
<inglise> Any Member State intending to grant compensatory aid shall adopt the necessary national measures within three months of the date of the Commission decision or the prior notification by the Member State provided for in paragraph 4. </inglise>
<eesti> Iga liikmesriik, kes kavatseb anda tasandustoetust, v&otilde;tab vajalikud siseriiklikud meetmed kolme kuu jooksul alates komisjoni otsuse kuup&auml;evast v&otilde;i l&otilde;ikes 4 etten&auml;htud eelnevast teatamisest. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 12 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 12 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Payment to the same beneficiary of an amount of the same compensatory aid instalment may not be made during the same budget year as payment of the corresponding amount of another instalment. </inglise>
