<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> Payment of the amount of the first instalment of compensatory aid as referred to in: </inglise>
<eesti> Tasandustoetuse esimese osamakse summa, millele osutatakse: </eesti>
<inglise> - Title II shall be made within one year following the date of the appreciable revaluation which gave entitlement to the aid concerned, </inglise>
