<inglise> - 12 months later in the case of recipients of amounts of a structural or environmental character, or </inglise>
<eesti> - 12 kuu p&auml;rast, juhul kui tegemist on struktuuri- v&otilde;i keskkonnakaitsesummade saajatega v&otilde;i </eesti>
<inglise> - nine months later in the case of recipients of other direct aid as referred to in Article 5(1) of Regulation (EC) No 2799/98. </inglise>
<eesti> - 9 kuu p&auml;rast, juhul kui tegemist on muude m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2799/98 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud otsetoetuste saajatega. </eesti>
<inglise> 3. </inglise>
<eesti> 3. </eesti>
<inglise> The time limits referred to in Article 11(1) and (5) and in paragraph 2 of this Article may be amended by the Commission at the duly justified request of Member States. </inglise>
