<inglise> Article 14 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 14 </eesti>
<inglise> Amounts quoted in tenders submitted in response to invitations to tender organised under an instrument forming part of the common agricultural policy shall, with the exception of amounts the Community contribution to which is financed from the EAGGF Guidance Section, be expressed in euros. </inglise>
