<inglise> Article 15 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 15 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The percentage of appreciability of an appreciable revaluation and the reduction in the exchange rate shall be expressed to three decimal places, the third decimal being rounded off. </inglise>
